file_content.text: You there! This area's restricted!
I'll bring Empress Vaylin your head!
You will face justice!
Fall before the might of the empire!
I won't fall! Not to you!
You will not take what is mine!
Zakuul belongs to me!
Empress, forgive me!
I am your executioner!
No... I cannot fail now...
This time, I destroy you!
This is the end, Outlander!
Steer clear of the Horizon Guard. If we're not careful, they'll see right through these disguises.
Look out. Horizon Guard.
I'm sorry, but the kitchen's off limits.
We've got clearance. You need confirmation, take it up with Indo Zal.
We're checking Vaylin's food for poison. Let us pass, or we'll arrest you for endangering the empress.
I'll take your word for it. I've had enough of Indo to last me a lifetime.
N-no need for that! Go right in.
No entry till shift change. Unless you've got our food order...
Anyone order food?
It's about time. Go on in, before they chew their arms off.
Captains only. Come back when you've gained a few ranks.
Stand back. Captains only.
I am a captain. Now let me pass, before I demote you to sanitation.
My apologies, sir! Make yourself at home.
Everything's in order, Captain.
A Knight Captain's shield. With any luck, this will get us behind closed doors.
Long live Empress Vaylin.
Rations for the guards. This might come in handy.
Try not to bother the cooks.
Sorry. You don't have access.
Captain.
Watch out. The beast master's in a worse mood than usual, if that's even possible.
The food's here!
Finally. Thanks for dropping it off.
Well, that was unexpected.
We need a distraction...
I have to admit, that was impressive.
